metadata.name: I Survived... #1
metadata.description:
Pop Punk and AB83 present "I Survived... 2022", a generative series documenting the wild year that was 2022. 

This collection consists of 222 pieces and launched in December of 2022. Every piece is based on a combination of events, people, PFPs and art. It recognizes that you made it through and survived!

Creators of the fine art (1/1, editions) included in the pieces can be found via Twitter using the trait name for Artist. Just add @ to the trait name when searching! PFP project names can be found via the "PFP" trait."

All rights are reserved to their respective creators and owners where applicable. This is an artistic, historical documentation of elements we experience in the NFT community. It was created in the spirit of fair use! Much love to you!
